h anything else, just exit:\\n\\ncurl -s 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=35.96&longitude=-83.92&hourly=temperature_2m,weathercode,precipitation,windspeed_10m,uv_index,relativehumidity_2m&daily=temperature_2m_max,temperature_2m_min,weathercode,uv_index_max,precipitation_sum,sunrise,sunset&current_weather=true&forecast_days=3&temperature_unit=fahrenheit&windspeed_unit=mph&precipitation_unit=inch&timezone=America%2FNew_York' -o /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json 2>&1 && echo 'Weather cache updated'\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777629731510,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777628831510,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 12,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777628831522\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1776886613764,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1776886613764\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\\n\\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD (with deduplication) ===\\nSTEP 4 - Read last seen ID: cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"0\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 5 - List iCloud emails (newest first): himalaya envelope list --account icloud 'order by date desc' 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\\n\\nSTEP 6 - For each email where ID > last_seen_ID:\\n  - Read it: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\\n  - Note its content for reporting\\n\\nSTEP 7 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\\n\\nSTEP 8 - After sending, update checkpoint: echo <highest_new_id> > ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt\\n\\nRULES:\\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\\n- ICLOUD: Only report emails with ID strictly greater than the saved last_icloud_id\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false,\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777630155136,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777626555136,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 20533,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliverySta