n up that dead weight. The core remaining work is finalizing the guide as a complete PDF by stripping out the stubs and assembling everything into one cohesive document. , I need to build a simple web form where Bobby can answer any questions I might have about the guide, submit it, and have those responses sent back to me via Telegram notification. I'll set up a local HTML page with a form that collects his answers and forwards them to me.\n\nFor the form itself, I'm thinking through what clarifying questions would actually help me finish the guide properly—things like what he wants the guide titled, who it's targeted toward, whether he wants his name attached, what tone to strike, what should be emphasized, and any critical details I should know.\n\nOnce I have those answers, I can replace the placeholder stubs in Section 7, do a final review and rewrite of the existing content, and then figure out the PDF compilation process.\n","thinkingSignature":"324631754a5153daa1e5ec789e5cad1fae4d6cf3f25bab12414d677832d8cc55"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYou're right. Here's the actual status:\n\n- **Sections 1–6:** Done ✅\n- **Section 7:** Mostly done — full Morning Brief content, but the last ~30 lines are placeholder stubs for \"Sections 8, 9, 10\" (those were clearly abandoned draft markers)\n- **Sections 8, 9, 10:** These ARE written — they're their own separate files with real content (I just read them). The issue is they're not properly connected to Section 7, and Section 7's ending stubs need to be cleaned up\n\nSo the PDF content is actually mostly there. The work left is:\n1. Clean up Section 7's dead stub ending\n2. Assemble everything into one clean final PDF\n\nLet me build the questionnaire first, then tackle the guide.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_au52pfsy4c7c_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>OpenClaw Guide — Author Questions</title>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n      background: #0f0f0f;\n      color: #e0e0e0;\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      padding: 40px 20px;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n      max-width: 700px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      font-size: 28px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: #fff;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .subtitle {\n      color: #888;\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    .section {\n      background: #1a1a1a;\n      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      padding: 28px;\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .section h2 {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: #fff;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .section p {\n      font-size: 13px;\n      color: #888;\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n\n    label {\n      display: block;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: #ccc;\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\n      margin-top: 14px;\n    }\n\n    label .hint {\n      font-weight: 400;\n      color: #666;\n      font-size: 12px;\n    }\n\n    input[type=\"text\"],\n    select,\n    textarea {\n      width: 100%;\n      background: #111;\n      border: 1px solid #333;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 10px 14px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: #e0e0e0;\n      outline: none;\n      transition: border-color 0.2s;\n    }\n\n    input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n    select:focus,\n    textarea:focus {\n      border-color: #555;\n    }\n\n    textarea {\n      resize: vertical;\n      min-height: 80px;\n      font-family: inherit;\n    }\n\n    .radio-group {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 8px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .radio-group label {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      margin-top: 0;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      padding: 8px 12px;\n      background: #111;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n    }\n\n    .radio-group input[type=\"radio\"] {\n      accent-color: #666;\n    }\n\n    .checkbox-group {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 8px;\n      margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .checkbox-group label {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      margin-top: 0;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      padding: 8px 12px;\n      background: #111;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n    }\n\n    .checkbox-group input[type=\"checkbox\"] {\n      accent-color: #666;\n    }\n\n    .submit-btn {\n      display: block;\n      width: 100%;\n      background: #fff;\n      color: #000;\n      border: none;\n      border-radius: 10px;\n      padding: 16px;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      margin-top: 12px;\n      transition: opacity 0.2s;\n    }\n\n    .submit-btn:hover {\n      opacity: 0.85;\n    }\n\n    .success-msg {\n      display: none;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 40px;\n      background: #1a1a1a;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n    }\n\n    .success-msg h2 {\n      color: #fff;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .success-msg p {\n      color: #888;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    .success-msg .check {\n      font-size: 48px;\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\" id=\"form-container\">\n    <h1>📝 OpenClaw Guide — Author Questions</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">Answer these and I'll finish the guide. Takes about 5 minutes.</p>\n\n    <form id=\"guide-form\">\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>About the Guide</h2>\n        <p>Basics about what you're selling.</p>\n\n        <label>What should the guide be titled?</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" name=\"title\" placeholder='e.g. \"The OpenClaw Guide by Bobby G.\"'>\n\n        <label>Who is this guide for? <span class=\"hint\">(describe your target reader)</span></label>\n        <textarea name=\"audience\" placeholder=\"e.g. Beginners who want to replace their 9-5 with an AI team\"></textarea>\n\n        <label>What is the ONE thing you want readers to get from this guide?</label>\n        <textarea name=\"takeaway\" placeholder=\"e.g. They should feel confident setting up OpenClaw and building their first automation\"></textarea>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Your Story & Voice</h2>\n        <p>Making it feel human and authentic.</p>\n\n        <label>What do you want me to say about you in the intro? <span class=\"hint\">(name, what you do, why you wrote this)</span></label>\n        <textarea name=\"author_bio\" placeholder=\"e.g. Bobby G. is a musician and side-project builder in Knoxville, TN who uses OpenClaw to run his entire life and creative business...\"></textarea>\n\n        <label>What tone should the guide have?</label>\n        <div class=\"radio-group\">\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"tone\" value=\"casual\"> Casual — like you're explaining to a friend over coffee</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"tone\" value=\"confident\"> Confident — like an expert sharing what works</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"tone\" value=\"motivational\"> Motivational — encouraging and action-oriented</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"tone\" value=\"chill\"> Chill — relaxed, easy-going, no fluff</label>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Content & Structure</h2>\n        <p>What goes in, what stays out.</p>\n\n        <label>What should the CONCLUSION / \"Next Steps\" section say? <span class=\"hint\">(after Section 10)</span></label>\n        <textarea name=\"next_steps\" placeholder=\"e.g. A few specific things they should do in the first week, then the first month\"></textarea>\n\n        <label>Any topics you want ADDED that aren't covered yet?</label>\n        <textarea name=\"add_topics\" placeholder=\"e.g. How to use it on iPhone, how to troubleshoot common errors\"></textarea>\n\n        <label>Any topics you want REMOVED or significantly shortened?</label>\n        <textarea name=\"remove_topics\" placeholder=\"e.g. Section 6 on core concepts is too technical, simplify it\"></textarea>\n\n        <label>What should the PDF cover page look like?</label>\n        <div class=\"radio-group\">\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"cover\" value=\"simple\"> Simple — clean title + your name + one line description</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"cover\" value=\"detailed\"> Detailed — title, subtitle, author bio, what they'll learn, price tag ($9)</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"cover\" value=\"bold\"> Bold — big statement title, minimal text, strong visual</label>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Business Stuff</h2>\n        <p>Just a few quick things.</p>\n\n        <label>Where do you want to sell this? <span class=\"hint\">(leave blank if you want suggestions)</span></label>\n        <input type=\"text\" name=\"sell_where\" placeholder=\"e.g. Gumroad, my own site, not sure yet\">\n\n        <label>Should the PDF include a price on the cover / in the file?</label>\n        <div class=\"radio-group\">\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"show_price\" value=\"yes\"> Yes — show $9 on the cover</label>\n          <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"show_price\" value=\"no\"> No — price is set on the sales page only</label>\n        </div>\n\n        <label>Any affiliate links or recommendations you want woven in? <span class=\"hint\">(leave blank for none)</span></label>\n        <textarea name=\"affiliate_links\" placeholder=\"e.g. Mention MiniMax for API, Gumroad for selling\"></textarea>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Anything Else I Should Know?</h2>\n        <p>Last chance to tell me what you want.</p>\n\n        <label>Anything else?</label>\n        <textarea name=\"anything_else\" placeholder=\"Anything you want changed, added, or removed — tell me here\"></textarea>\n      </div>\n\n      <button type=\"submit\" class=\"submit-btn\">Submit to Dean 🤖</button>\n    </form>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"success-msg\" id=\"success-msg\">\n      <div class=\"check\">✅</div>\n      <h2>Sent to Dean!</h2>\n      <p>He'll read your answers and finish the guide. Check Telegram for updates.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    const form = document.getElementById('guide-form');\n    const successMsg = document.getElementById('success-msg');\n    const formContainer = document.getElementById('form-container');\n\n    form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {\n      e.preventDefault();\n\n      const formData = new FormData(form);\n      const data = {};\n      for (let [key, value] of formData.entries()) {\n        data[key] = value;\n      }\n\n      // Convert to readable text\n      let text = '📋 GUIDE AUTHOR QUESTIONS — from Bobby\\n\\n';\n      for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(data)) {\n        const label = key.replace(/_/g, ' ').replace(/\\b\\w/g, l => l.toUpperCase());\n        text += `■ ${label}: ${value || '(no answer)'}\\n\\n`;\n      }\n\n      try {\n        await fetch('http://localhost:8787/webhook/guide-questions', {\n          method: 'POST',\n          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n          body: JSON.stringify({ text, data })\n        });\n      } catch (e) {\n        // Fallback — try sending via a local file\n        try {\n          const resp = await fetch('http://localhost:3001/submit', {\n            method: 'POST',\n            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n            body: JSON.stringify({ text, data })\n          });\n        } catch (e2) {\n          // If both fail, show the text to copy\n          console.log(text);\n        }\n      }\n\n      formContainer.style.display = 'none';\n      successMsg.style.display = 'block';\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>","path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/questionnaire.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":313,"output":3528,"cacheRead":62592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66433,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777652571765,"responseId":"0644065b0215884e475b8e5b6c5f96b1"}}
