{"type":"message","id":"1b319141","parentId":"21d1c1ee","timestamp":"2026-05-01T16:56:11.018Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I sent the voice memo. Now I should also update my rules to reflect that Bobby prefers shorter, more conversational replies, and voice memos as the default for longer messages.\n","thinkingSignature":"a8f065b6f0e663c0cf9f73205e2d09e1c2d7e46e37eb80ca9adc36753cc0e56d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nDone — that's what you'll get from me going forward. Casual, quick, easy to reply to.\n\nNext step — fill out the questionnaire so I can finish the guide:\n[http://192.168.1.162:8790/questionnaire.html](http://192.168.1.162:8790/questionnaire.html)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":176,"output":109,"cacheRead":78208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777654564188,"responseId":"06440e24634c962dc21505d49ee1cc1e"}}
