{"type":"message","id":"dd717062","parentId":"4fd9ddd5","timestamp":"2026-05-01T19:29:07.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the HTTP server is running on 8790 now. Both servers should be running:- port 8790: serves the HTML file\n- port 8791: handles the API (messages, replies, audio)\n","thinkingSignature":"f5a8aa0e8c6bd5ec6e49b7f4db7851acc0b5fcb663067c301bf8f97cba6f95cf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBoth servers are up:\n- **8790** — serves the Telephone page ✅\n- **8791** — handles messages and audio ✅\n\nTry the link now:\n[http://localhost:8790/telephone.html](http://localhost:8790/telephone.html)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65,"output":105,"cacheRead":98112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777663745080,"responseId":"06443201834e1dde3139cd81a3539005"}}
